        <div class="mb-16">
          <p class="text-teal text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">What You Gain</p>
          <h2 id="outcomes-heading" class="font-heading text-heading text-slate-900 font-bold max-w-lg">
            Real outcomes. Measurable impact.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 max-w-md">
            Synq doesn't add complexity — it removes the gaps where revenue was already slipping away.
