          <h2 id="pricing-heading" class="font-heading text-heading text-slate-900 font-bold max-w-xl">
            Flexible AI Front Desk Pricing
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-500 max-w-lg">
            Start with the chatbot your business needs, then add missed-call SMS or AI voice support when you're ready.
